215
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,510
I'm a prince too.

216
00:11:50,560 --> 00:11:53,270
But he is the Heir Apparent,
the future Emperor!

217
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:07,600
Jiang Leyao,

218
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,390
I misjudged you.

219
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:11,270
What about your dreams?

220
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,670
You're just...

221
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:17,270
another commoner chasing favor.

222
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,470
Let Beasts Garden know.

223
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,950
There's a newcomer arriving.

224
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,390
(Xiao Jingyou,)

225
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:42,430
(I've got nothing left to lose.)

226
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:45,070
(It's time you paid what you owe.)

